[name]
check_ssmtp

[info]
Checks status of a Secure SMTP  server.
[why]
To see status of your secure SMTP mailserver.
[how]
Connects to a secure SMTP server and checks status. Lets you specify expected responce string. You can also run a command and specify thresholds on responstime.
[platforms]
Not platform dependent.

